       <ProductDescription ID="36421746" LongDesc="&lt;b&gt;On-Counter High Performance Bar Code Reader&lt;/b&gt;\nThe Magellan™ 3200VSi bar code reader brings Datalogic’s new imaging technology to the high-volume point-of-sale. It is the first bar code scanner to duplicate the speed and wide field-of-view of high-performance omnidirectional laser scanners while adding the benefits associated with imaging. This imaging technology provides outstanding performance when capturing hard-to-read bar codes such as truncated (short), out-of-spec, poorly printed and GS1 DataBar™ codes, and provides support for both linear (1D) and 2D label decoding. The Magellan 3200VSi imager enables both sweep and presentation scanning techniques ensuring maximum productivity and ergonomic ease.\n\nWith the renowned quality and reliability famous in all Magellan products, the Magellan 3200VSi imager achieves new levels of product reliability by utilizing a solid-state design that does not require the use of laser modules or spinning motors, ensuring years of worry-free operation.\n\nUnique features not found on any point-of-sale scanner, include a Micro-SD card reader to help with software management, upgrading, and maintenance. Managing software with the Magellan 3200VSi reader is very flexible and includes multiple methods to load new software or to modify existing configuration files and application firmware. Because most of the Magellan 3200VSi scanner features are software based, new capabilities are simple to add, even after the initial installation, increasing the useful life of the scanner and protecting your company’s technology investment over time.\n\nOther Magellan product features include Diagnostics Reporting, Host Download and Productivity Index Reporting™ allowing management to use data from the scanner to improve throughput and manage maintenance. Datalogic’s Illumix™ intelligent illumination technology optimizes light levels to capture images and read bar codes from mobile phones, PDAs or computer display screens." This robust solution provides integrated deduplication, granular restore features, open file protection, disaster recovery and backup protection for Microsoft Exchange, SharePoint Services, SQL and Windows workstations.\n\n&lt;b&gt;Key Features&lt;/b&gt;\n- Optimized data protection for Windows Small Business Server Standard or Premium Editions.\n- Integrated and adaptable deduplication (using NetBackup PureDisk technology).\n- First-to-market granular recovery for Exchange, SQL and Active Directory environments running in a VMware and Hyper-V environment.\n- Patent-pending Granular Recovery Technology (GRT) recovers critical Microsoft application data in seconds.\n- Centralized 3-tier set-up, reporting and patch management.\n- Scalable heterogeneous support through remote Agents and Options.\n- Continuous data protection.\n- Innovative multi-product integration with market leading technologies.\n\n&lt;b&gt;Key Benefits&lt;/b&gt;\n- Comprehensive data protection for Microsoft Windows Small Business Server 2008 and 2003 with disk or tape storage support.\n- Reduce storage costs while optimizing network utilization across physical and virtual environments through integrated deduplication and archiving technology.\n- Eliminate redundant backups for Microsoft Exchange, Active Directory, and SQL in a virtual environment with integrated VMware and Hyper-V backup protection.\n- Restore individual Exchange messages, SharePoint site items or documents, and Active Directory user preferences from a single-pass backup.\n- High-powered Backup Exec remote Agents and Options extend data protection to Linux, Unix, Mac and Netware environments.\n- Backup Exec replication technology helps ensure data changes are continuously backed up from remote servers."        <ProductDescription ID="22073254" LongDesc="   The OmniView PRO3 USB &amp; PS/2 KVM Switch provides easy and dependable server control with extraordinary performance. The Switch enables network administrators to monitor and control up to four, eight, or 16 USB- and PS/2-platform servers from a single console. The PRO Series KVM Switches are the industry's most popular for small-to-medium server rooms, branch locations, and test and development labs. Designed to grow along with your server network, the Switch can be daisy-chained together using dedicated daisy chain ports with other OmniView PRO Series KVM or SMB KVM Switches to support up to 256 servers.\n\n&lt;b&gt;Advantages&lt;/b&gt;\n\n-Dual-Port Cabling reduces cable bulk by 55% when compared to conventional KVM cabling by connecting two servers per cable.\n-USB &amp; PS/2 compatibility gives expanded connectivity in a mixed server environment.\n-Dedicated Daisy-Chain ports let you expand your KVM configuration without sacrificing CPU ports.\n-Saves setup time and simplifies viewing and switching between multiple servers with OSD.\n-Provides continuous server monitoring with programmable AutoScan and hot keys.\n-Ensures consistent compatibility with flash-upgradeable firmware."    <ReasonsToBuy/>
   <ProductBundled/>
       <ProductDescription ID="27309726" LongDesc="The Cisco UCS C210 M2 server is a general purpose, 2-socket, 2 rack unit (RU) rack-mount server that balances performance, density, and efficiency for storage-intensive workloads. The system is built for applications such as network file servers and appliances, storage servers, database servers, and content-delivery servers.\n\nBuilding on the success of the UCS C210 M1 server, the UCS C210 M2 server extends the capabilities of the Cisco Unified Computing System, using Intel's latest Xeon 5600 Series multicore processors to deliver even better performance and efficiency.\n\n- Up to two Intel Xeon 5600 Series multicore processors\n- Up to 96 GB of industry-standard double data rate (DDR3) main memory\n- Up to 16 internal small form-factor (SFF), SAS, or SATA disk drives; up to 8 TB total\n- Built-in RAID 0 and 1 support for up to four SATA drives; RAID 0 and 1 support for up to four SAS or SATA drives with optional mezzanine card; and RAID 0, 1, 5, 6, 10, 50, and 60 support for up to 16 SAS or SATA drives with up to two optional LSI MegaRAID Controllers\n- Five full-height PCI Express (PCIe) slots: two full-height, full-length x8 PCIe card slots and three full-height, half-length x8 PCI card slots, all with x16 connectors" ManualPDFSize="0" ManualPDFURL="" PDFSize="0" PDFURL="" ShortDesc="UCS C210 M2 General-Purpose Rack-Mount Server, 2U, 1x Xeon E5506, 2.13 GHz, RAM 4 GB, SAS, hot-swap 2.5&quot;, DVD±RW, MGA G200, Gigabit Ethernet" URL="http://www.cisco.com/en/US/products/ps10889/index.html" WarrantyInfo="" langid="1"/>

    <ProductDescription ID="40663828" LongDesc="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: larger; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;HP ProLiant ML350e Gen8 v2は、インテル® Xeon® プロセッサー E5-2400 v2製品ファミリーを搭載し、12個のDIMMスロット、最大6つのPCIスロットと、十分な拡張性を装備しつつ、コストパフォーマンスに優れたタワーサーバーの定番です。ノンホットプラグ3.5型ドライブ最大4台、ホットプラグ3.5型ドライブ最大8台、ホットプラグ2.5型ドライブ最大16台を搭載出来る合計3つの製品をラインアップ致します。また、標準装備のiLO Management Engine (iLO 4) がサーバーのライフサイクル管理を自動化し、サーバー運用の劇的な効率改善に寄与します。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: larger; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Features&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;b&gt;優れた性能と拡張性&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;インテル® Xeon® プロセッサー E5-2400 v2製品ファミリーを最大2基、12個のDDR3 DIMMスロットによる最大192GBメモリ、ノンホットプラグ対応の3.5型SATAドライブ4台、ホットプラグ対応の3.5型SAS/SATA/SSDドライブを最大8台、または2.5型を最大16台搭載可能、ディスクコントローラーは定評のSmartアレイB120iを標準装備、PCIスロットは最大6スロット装備可能です。PCI Express 3.0にも対応。優れた性能と拡張性であらゆる用途に対応します。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;高度なライフサイクル管理機能をサーバーに組み込み&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;iLO Management Engine (iLO 4)が標準で搭載され、これまでのiLOで提供されていた高速なリモートコンソール機能やメディアマウント機能に加え、サーバーのライフサイクルを管理するための様々な管理機能が組み込まれます。サーバーの導入作業を自動化し、メディアレスセットアップやファームウェア/ドライバの自動更新を実現する「Intelligent Provisioning」、ハードウェア単体での監視を実現し、OS上のエージェントソフトウェアを不要にする「Agentless Management」、サーバー内部の状況を全て記録し、問題解決を迅速化する「Active Health System」といった高度な運用支援機能により、お客様の運用コストを大幅に削減します。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;独自の省電力技術で省エネに貢献&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;80 PLUSの「Platinum」を取得した、AC/DC変換効率最大94%の高効率電源を更に改良し、力率改善により更なる節電効果を実現する「Platinum Plus」パワーサプライに対応。大量の温度センサーを更に増強して内部温度のきめ細かな把握と、必要な箇所だけ冷やすスマートな冷却により、無駄な電力を使わない「センサーの海」を実装。動的消費電力上限（HP Dynamic Power Capping）機能により、各サーバーの消費電力の上限を任意に設定可能。これらにより与えられた電力容量内により多くのサーバーを安心して稼動させることが出来ます。Gen8は従来製品から定評をいただいているこれらHP独自技術を更に強化して省エネに貢献します。\n" ManualPDFSize="0" ManualPDFURL="" PDFSize="0" PDFURL="" ShortDesc="HP ProLiant ML350e Gen8 v2 E5-2420v2 1.9GHz 6-core 1P 4GB-U 460W PS Server/Promo" URL="" WarrantyInfo="標準保証: 3年間翌営業日オンサイトサービス、3年間パーツ保証\n" langid="26"/>

<FeatureLogo ID="5" Feature_ID="8400" Value="Gold" LogoPic="http://images.icecat.biz/img/feature_logo/5-2841.png" Width="200" Height="127" Size="76132">
        <Descriptions>
            <Description ID="5" langid="1">
                <![CDATA[EPEAT® is a comprehensive environmental rating that helps identify greener computers and other electronic equipment. EPEAT®-registered electronic products meet environmental measures referred to as criteria. All of the criteria used in EPEAT are based on ANSI-approved public standards, which provide technical details for every criterion and specify how a manufacturer must demonstrate compliance.\n\nThe EPEAT Gold rating means that the product meets all required criteria plus 75% of the optional criteria.]]>
            </Description>
            <Description ID="27" langid="2">
                <![CDATA[EPEAT® is een allesomvattende milieubeoordeling (van wieg-tot-graf-benadering) die ondersteunt bij het kiezen van groenere computers en andere elektronische apparatuur. Bij EPEAT® geregistreerde elektronische producten voldoen aan milieu-eisen, gebaseerd op ANSI-standaarden. Voor iedere eis is gespecificeerd hoe een fabrikant compliance moet demonstreren.\n\nDe EPEAT Gold-beoordeling houdt in dat het product aan alle verplichte eisen voldoet en aan meer dan 75% van com optionele criteria tegemoet komt.]]>
            </Description>

Les produits électroniques enregistrés EPEAT ® répondent aux mesures environnementales mentionnées comme critères. Tous les critères utilisés dans EPEAT sont basées sur des normes publiques approuvées par ANSI, qui fournit des détails techniques pour chaque critère et précise comment le fabricant doit démontrer la conformité.\n\nLa note EPEAT Gold signifie que le produit répond à tous les critères requis et 75% des critères facultatifs.]]>
            </Description>
            <Description ID="79" langid="4">

EPEAT® registrierte elektronische Produkte erfüllen ökologische Maßnahmen, sogenannte Kriterien. Alle EPEAT Kriterien basieren auf ANSI-geprüften öffentlichen Standards , die technische Details für jedes einzelne Kriterium zur Verfügung stellen und angeben, wie ein  Hersteller die Einhaltung nachweisen muss. \n\nDas EPEAT Gold Rating bedeutet, dass das Produkt alle geforderten Kriterien plus 75% der optionalen Kriterien erfüllt.]]>

Tutti i criteri utilizzati nel EPEAT sono basati su standard pubblici approvati dall'ANSI, che fornisce i dettagli tecnici e specifica come i produttori debbano dimostrare l'avvenuta conformità.             <Description ID="1" langid="1">
                <![CDATA[Bluetooth is a proprietary open wireless technology standard for exchanging data over short distances (using short-wavelength radio transmissions in the ISM band from 2400–2480 MHz) from fixed and mobile devices, creating personal area networks (PANs) with high levels of security.]]>
            </Description>
            <Description ID="6" langid="2">

Dankzij Bluetooth kunnen bijvoorbeeld adresgegevens tussen mobiele telefoons worden uitgewisseld, kan snel vanaf een handheld computer worden geprint, of kan een mobiele telefoon worden uitgerust met een draadloze headset.]]>
            </Description>
            <Description ID="54" langid="3">
                <![CDATA[Bluetooth est une norme standard com technologie sans fil pour échanger des données sur com courtes distances (avec les transmissions radio com courte longueur d'onde sur la bande ISM 2400-2480 MHz) d’appareils fixes et mobiles en créant une zone com réseaux personnels (PAN) avec des niveaux élevés com sécurité.]]>

            </Description>

            </Description>

            </Description>

	  <SummaryDescription>
	    <ShortSummaryDescription >Samsung NP270E5E ATIV, Notebook, Black, Clamshell, 1.1, Intel Celeron, BGA1023</ShortSummaryDescription>
